jtorrent.tracker

Class JTracker.TorrentRef

  • java.lang.Object
    • jtorrent.common.JTorrent
      • jtorrent.tracker.JTracker.TorrentRef
  • Enclosing class:
    JTracker

    public class JTracker.TorrentRef
extends JTorrent
    A tracker's reference to a torrent. This reference will contain a list of peers that are actively using this torrent.
